      "title": "New Day Dawning!",
      "internalName": "CH - first evar",
      "description": "You have just arrived in the Ark Bay 313, on your way to the Hestia Back Range, a training and testing ground for the Hestia Company.  \n\nYou will need to achieve your Hestia ID in order to be cleared for passage to Ascent Station, the first stop for all new freelancers.",
