      "description": "OK then, looks like everything is in order. [$imp]Check in with Kelly Sweet[$/imp] on the [$loc]Emergence Terrace[$/loc]. She will get you on your way. \n\nAs you\u0027ll see on your drive, we\u0027ve got osterakes breeding out of control in the caves. I\u0027m sure no one would mind if their population thinned out a bit. [$emote]Rogers smirks.[$/emote]\n\n[$inst]The orange arrow at the top of the screen is a Waypoint arrow. It points toward your next mission objective. To reach your next objective, follow the arr\u2026",
